helium (0.6.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Update included gupnp-av, use a git submodule
    - Fix issues with casing in LastChange XML.
  * Fix an issue with the generated DIDLLite XML
  * Fix some weird UI behaviour in renderer view
  * Add a fallback icon for unknown resources
  * Add a tooltip when seeking and improve general usability
  * Cleanup gupnp <-> Qt bridge code
  * Don't display some uninteresting error messages
  * Fix several leaks and crashes
  * Add filtering to browse view. Browse lists can now be filtered by title or
    meta-data
  * Use name of selected renderer in context menu
  * Add version to "About" page
  * Fix postinst script to properly set GConf keys
  * Add logging of UPnP traffic

 -- Jens Georg <mail+helium@jensge.org>  Sun, 16 Jun 2012 12:49:34 +0200

helium (0.5.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Restart the network connection when user taps on refresh
  * Update included gupnp-av
  * Several layer interaction fixes
  * Player volume control
  * Add option to enable on-device media sharing if available
  * Add settings page
  * Lot of code simplification

 -- Jens Georg <mail+helium@jensge.org>  Mon, 04 Jun 2012 21:18:50 +0200

